---
// Figure: Revocation state model
// Five core states — Active, Suspended, Revoked, Expired, Reissued.
// Minimal transitions. Note below the diagram (not inside it) about
// deletion, erasure, and administrative revocation being distinct operations.
---

<div class="reveal my-12 md:my-16">
  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border overflow-hidden" style="background: rgba(11,11,17,0.6);">
    <div class="p-6 md:p-8">

      <div class="mb-6">
        <p class="text-text-tertiary text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-1">Credential lifecycle</p>
        <h3 class="text-text-primary font-display font-bold text-lg tracking-tight">Revocation state model</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full overflow-x-auto">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 780 260" class="w-full min-w-[620px]" role="img" aria-label="State machine with five states: active, suspended, revoked, expired, reissued, linked by minimal transitions.">
          <defs>
            <marker id="rsm-arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto-start-reverse">
              <path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.6)"/>
            </marker>
          </defs>

          <!-- Active -->
          <g>
            <rect x="40" y="100" width="140" height="54" rx="10" fill="rgba(74,222,128,0.08)" stroke="rgba(74,222,128,0.6)" stroke-width="1.3"/>
            <text x="110" y="125" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.9)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="13" font-weight="600">Active</text>
            <text x="110" y="141" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.55)" font-family="'Inter', system-ui" font-size="10">valid · checkable</text>
          </g>

          <!-- Suspended -->
          <g>
            <rect x="230" y="40" width="140" height="54" rx="10" fill="rgba(245,158,11,0.08)" stroke="rgba(245,158,11,0.55)" stroke-width="1.3"/>
            <text x="300" y="64" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.9)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="13" font-weight="600">Suspended</text>
            <text x="300" y="80" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.55)" font-family="'Inter', system-ui" font-size="10">hold pending review</text>
          </g>

          <!-- Revoked -->
          <g>
            <rect x="230" y="170" width="140" height="54" rx="10" fill="rgba(239,68,68,0.08)" stroke="rgba(239,68,68,0.55)" stroke-width="1.3"/>
            <text x="300" y="194" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.9)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="13" font-weight="600">Revoked</text>
            <text x="300" y="210" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.55)" font-family="'Inter', system-ui" font-size="10">administrative termination</text>
          </g>

          <!-- Expired -->
          <g>
            <rect x="420" y="100" width="140" height="54" rx="10" fill="rgba(160,160,180,0.08)" stroke="rgba(160,160,180,0.55)" stroke-width="1.3"/>
            <text x="490" y="125" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.9)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="13" font-weight="600">Expired</text>
            <text x="490" y="141" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.55)" font-family="'Inter', system-ui" font-size="10">validity ended</text>
          </g>

          <!-- Reissued -->
          <g>
            <rect x="610" y="100" width="140" height="54" rx="10" fill="rgba(167,139,250,0.08)" stroke="rgba(167,139,250,0.55)" stroke-width="1.3"/>
            <text x="680" y="125" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.9)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="13" font-weight="600">Reissued</text>
            <text x="680" y="141" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.55)" font-family="'Inter', system-ui" font-size="10">fresh credential</text>
          </g>

          <!-- Minimal transitions -->
          <!-- Active → Suspended -->
          <line x1="170" y1="115" x2="230" y2="75" stroke="rgba(232,232,240,0.55)" stroke-width="1.2" marker-end="url(#rsm-arrow)"/>
          <!-- Suspended → Revoked -->
          <line x1="300" y1="94" x2="300" y2="170" stroke="rgba(232,232,240,0.55)" stroke-width="1.2" marker-end="url(#rsm-arrow)"/>
          <!-- Suspended → Active (cleared) -->
          <path d="M 230 75 Q 195 95 170 115" fill="none" stroke="rgba(232,232,240,0.35)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3" marker-end="url(#rsm-arrow)"/>
          <!-- Active → Expired -->
          <line x1="180" y1="127" x2="420" y2="127" stroke="rgba(232,232,240,0.55)" stroke-width="1.2" marker-end="url(#rsm-arrow)"/>
          <!-- Expired → Reissued -->
          <line x1="560" y1="127" x2="610" y2="127" stroke="rgba(232,232,240,0.55)" stroke-width="1.2" marker-end="url(#rsm-arrow)"/>
          <!-- Revoked → Reissued (successful appeal, dashed) -->
          <path d="M 370 197 Q 525 220 680 154" fill="none" stroke="rgba(232,232,240,0.35)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3" marker-end="url(#rsm-arrow)"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="text-text-tertiary text-sm mt-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
    Deletion from a device, erasure of retained personal data, and administrative revocation of credential validity are different operations and should not be collapsed into one concept.
  </p>
</div>
